data.description: Welcome home to 1751 Progress St! This well layed out 4 bed 2 bath 1600 square foot home has been updated with LVP flooring throughout the living space and new carpet in the bedrooms. The kitchen has been updated with granite counterops, tile backsplash and new appliances. As you walk from the covered front porch through the front door into the living room you feel at home with the open concept that flows into the dining room and kitchen. There are two bedrooms and one full bath on either side of the home. The utility room is quite large which is quite nice! There are two doors on the rear of the home that open to a large screened in porch for you to enjoy the South Carolina weather. There is a 12x12 ft storage room that comes with the property for all your extra things. Come make 1751 Progress Street home!
